column3: from here on: manually added missing NUTS-3 regions as per „Regions in the European Union NUTS2016/EU-28, edition 2018“ (KS-GQ-18-007-EN-N.pdf) & map on https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/web/coastal-island-outermost-regions/background
updates according to changes from NUTS2016 to NUTS2021 classifications incorporated (including some further NUTS-3 regions that were irrelevant before)
